name: 2014 Wall Calendars
description:
The 4th year running! 

- High quality environmentally sustainable FSC paper 
- Saddle-stitch binding 
- Oversized at 9.5" x 12.25" closed, 19" long x 12.25" across when open 
- 12 frameable art prints of my favourite 2013 original paintings 
- Includes all major dates, as well as many International and special dates 
- Includes moon phases and inspirational quotes 
- Comes individually packaged with protective cardboard insert 
- Printed in Canada
- Limited edition, only 250 printed

BONUS OFFER
For a limited time until January 15th, I'm offering up my 2014 Wall Calendar for $25, which includes International Shipping, any applicable Taxes, plus a postcard and a greeting card (for a total value of $40). LIMITED QUANTITIES AVAILABLE! Orders yours today to receive it before Christmas, while also supporting my upcoming year with my mobile studio, The Painted Road Project, at the same time. Many Thanks, Daina

ORDER HERE: https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-painted-road-project/contributions/new?perk_amt=25&perk_id=1523195

name: Collage: Map of Atlantic Ocean + Wave (6)
description:
Each 6”x6” digital collage is mounted onto a 1-1/2” deep cradled wood panel. The edges are stained for a warm, rich effect, and the final product is varnished and fashioned with hardware, ready to hang. 

Each design is created using a bathymetric map (of the North Atlantic between New England and Nova Scotia) and a cut-out of an original oil painting by Daina Scarola printed using pure pigment inks on fine art paper. The panel is made using the fast-growing Paulownia tree hardwood.

USA Bathymetric Map of Atlantic Ocean

Options: 3/4" unstained wood panel
